{"word":"H7771 - שֹׁועַ - shôwaʻ - sho'-ah - Bountiful","slug":"H7771","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שֹׁועַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shôwaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sho'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bountiful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05E2; - sho&#x0302;a&#x201B;</b> - <i>sho'-ah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7768\">H7768</a> in the original sense of <i>freedom</i>; a <i>noble</i>, that is, <i>liberal</i>, <i>opulent</i>; also (as noun in the derived sense) a <i>halloo: - </i>bountiful, crying, rich."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7768\">H7768</a>, <a href=\"#/H7772\">H7772</a>, <a href=\"#/H7773\">H7773</a>, <a href=\"#/H7775\">H7775</a>"}]}